---
title: Smothered Pepper Jack Burgers with Spicy Ketchup & BBQ Potato Wedges
description: This burger stacks up against the best, literally: Each bun holds a turkey patty that’s been smothered in melted pepper jack cheese AND sautéed peppers and onions. Just in case that doesn’t make this burger a front-runner for first-place, let’s introduce the secret weapon: a special spicy ketchup with hot sauce that you can add to taste. If you aren’t blown away yet, you will be when you’re holding this bad boy in your hands.
